  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"z5tNPm0k\">想起一次与前男友的闲聊。</p><p data-pid=\"Qda4P6VJ\">“如果有下辈子，换我来当男生，那你就当女生，我们依然在一起。”</p><p data-pid=\"0SGM9Yvm\">他嗯额哦没有正面回答，想要敷衍着过去。</p><p data-pid=\"gX5HZjEa\">我却认真了，说“如果我是男生了，你还是男生，还在一起，不就成基佬了？怪怪的呢（希望同性恋别太敏感，这是绝大多数性取向正常的人会有的想法。）”</p><p data-pid=\"3DgPUQyl\">“可我还是想做男生。”</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br></p><p data-pid=\"kz5hdwRu\">我也想当男生！</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f3120e89c6edb834f8a0a24b541c1293_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"512\" data-rawheight=\"512\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-75d44786a9c76c99b16d9f718025edbd\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f3120e89c6edb834f8a0a24b541c1293_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"512\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f3120e89c6edb834f8a0a24b541c1293_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='512' height='512'></svg>\" data-rawwidth=\"512\" data-rawheight=\"512\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-75d44786a9c76c99b16d9f718025edbd\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-f3120e89c6edb834f8a0a24b541c1293_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"512\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-f3120e89c6edb834f8a0a24b541c1293_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-f3120e89c6edb834f8a0a24b541c1293_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p></p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
